etter on constrained budget hosts.','This may take several minutes to complete.'=>'This may take several minutes to complete.','Keep this window open and do not close during the build process.'=>'Keep this window open and do not close during the build process.','- Switch to the %s which requires a capable hosting provider (VPS recommended).'=>'- Switch to the %s which requires a capable hosting provider (VPS recommended).','- In %s consider adding file/directory or database table filters.'=>'- In %s consider adding file/directory or database table filters.','- In the \'Size Checks\' section above consider adding filters (if notice is shown).'=>'- In the \'Size Checks\' section above consider adding filters (if notice is shown).','- Add data filters to get the package size under %s: '=>'- Add data filters to get the package size under %s: ','Total size and row counts are approximate values.  The thresholds that trigger notices are %1$s records total for the entire database.  Larger databases take more time to process.  On some budget hosts that have cpu/memory/timeout limits this may cause issues.'=>'Total size and row counts are approximate values.  The thresholds that trigger notices are %1$s records total for the entire database.  Larger databases take more time to process.  On some budget hosts that have cpu/memory/timeout limits this may cause issues.','Auto File Filters'=>'Auto File Filters','Auto Directory Filters'=>'Auto Directory Filters','ZipArchive Engine'=>'ZipArchive Engine','Step 1'=>'Step 1','The build can\'t continue because the total size of files and the database exceeds the %s limit that can be processed when creating a DupArchive package. '=>'The build can\'t continue because the total size of files and the database exceeds the %s limit that can be processed when creating a DupArchive package. ','The total size of the site (files plus  database).'=>'The total size of the site (files plus database).','Total Size:'=>'Total Size:','The notices for tables are %1$s records or names with upper-case characters.  Individual tables will not trigger a notice message, but can help narrow down issues if they occur later on.'=>'The notices for tables are %1$s records or names with upper-case characters.  Individual tables will not trigger a notice message, but can help narrow down issues if they occur later on.','Option 1: DupArchive'=>'Option 1: DupArchive','PHP is unable to read the following items and they will NOT be included in the package.  Please work with your host to adjust the permissions or resolve the symbolic-link(s) shown in the lists below.  If these items are not needed then this notice can be ignored.'=>'PHP is unable to read the following items and they will NOT be included in the package.  Please work with your host to adjust the permissions or resolve the symbolic-link(s) shown in the lists below.  If these items are not needed then this notice can be ignored.','If this environment/system and the system where it will be installed are set up to support Unicode and long paths then these filters can be ignored.  If you run into issues with creating or installing a package, then is recommended to filter these paths.'=>'If this environment/system and the system where it will be installed are set up to support Unicode and long paths then these filters can be ignored.  If you run into issues with creating or installing a package, then is recommended to filter these paths.','An "Addon Site" is a separate WordPress site(s) residing in subdirectories within this site. If you confirm these to be separate sites, 
